NK033(gi)006:1: // 'od gsal rdzogs pa chen po man ngag sde'i gnad
NK033(gi)006:2: kyi bcud phud sangs rgyas kyi 'das rjes gsum bzhugs
NK033(gi)006:4: bud+d+ha d+he ka ra ye d+hu n+aa ma /
NK033(gi)006:6: sangs rgyas kyi zhal chems dang po zhes bya ba /
NK033(gi)006:7: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas drug pa rdo rje 'chang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)006:9: rigs kyi bu rnams gsang sngags kyi gnad thams cad gcig tu dril nas nyams su longs shig /
NK033(gi)006:10: lus ngag yid kyi sngon 'gro ni //
NK033(gi)006:11: mi rtag snying rje byang sems sbyangs //
NK033(gi)006:12: lus 'di ma rig rgyus bskyed phyir //
NK033(gi)006:13: rigs drug sa bon nyid du gnas //
NK033(gi)006:14: rig pa sku gsum dngos yin phyir //
NK033(gi)006:15: sku gsum yi ge gsum du shar //
NK033(gi)006:16: yi ge'i rtsal sbyang ru shan dbye //
NK033(gi)006:17: de nas rnal du dbab pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)006:18: nyan thos byang sems khro bo yi //
NK033(gi)006:19: lta ltangs nyid kyis sor yang gzhug /
NK033(gi)006:20: gnas brtan grol ba'i gding thob nas //
NK033(gi)006:21: phyi nang bya ba kun btang ste //
NK033(gi)006:22: glang seng drang srong 'dug stangs bca' //
NK033(gi)006:23: ngag ni smra ba rgyun bcad la //
NK033(gi)006:24: sems ni smin phrag mkha' la gtad //
NK033(gi)006:25: sgo yul rlung gi gnad bstun pas //
NK033(gi)006:26: yul la ye shes mngon du snang //
NK033(gi)006:27: mngon sum gnad las 'bral mi bya //
NK033(gi)006:28: mi 'gul gsum la gzhi bcas pas //
NK033(gi)006:29: snang ba bzhi yi drod rnyed nas //
NK033(gi)006:30: sdod pa gsum gyi tshad zin te //
NK033(gi)006:31: thob pa gsum gyi gzer thebs na //
NK033(gi)006:32: khams gsum dag tu ldog re kan //
NK033(gi)006:33: mya ngan 'da' bar the tshom med //
NK033(gi)006:34: ces sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lho phyogs sman 'tsho byed gzhon nu'i ldum rar /
NK033(gi)006:35: rdo rje 'chang chen po yongs su mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul bstan pa'i tshe /
NK033(gi)006:36: dga' rab rdo rje sa la 'gyel zhing gdung ba'i smre sngags phyungs pa /
NK033(gi)006:37: kye ma kyi hud kye ma klong //
NK033(gi)006:38: ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub na //
NK033(gi)006:39: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK033(gi)006:40: zhes brjod de brgyal sangs pa dang //
NK033(gi)006:41: 'od phung gi nang nas phyag g.yas pa'i gru mo man chad phyung nas /
NK033(gi)006:42: rin po che shel gyi za ma tog sen gang ba zhig /
NK033(gi)006:43: phyag g.yas pa'i mthil du babs te //
NK033(gi)006:44: de zhal phye bas rin po che mthing kha la
NK033(gi)006:45: beed+aur+ya bzhu ba'i khu bas bris pa babs pas dga'
NK033(gi)006:46: rab rdo rje rtogs pa'i gding dang ldan par gyur
NK033(gi)006:49: bud+d+ha d+he ka ra ma du n+aa ma /
NK033(gi)006:51: sangs rgyas kyi 'das rjes gnyis pa /
NK033(gi)006:52: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dbang po'i stobs
NK033(gi)006:53: kyis rnam par gnon pa nyid la phyag 'tshal lo
NK033(gi)006:54: // nges par sangs rgyas thob 'dod na //
NK033(gi)006:55: sngon du 'gro la rtsal nyid sbyang //
NK033(gi)006:56: lus dang ngag dang yid gsum po //
NK033(gi)006:57: ru shan legs par ma phyed na //
NK033(gi)006:58: khams gsum nyid las mi grol bas //
NK033(gi)006:59: sngon du 'gro ba dag la bslab //
NK033(gi)006:60: sngon 'gro'i gnad la mkhas gyur na //
NK033(gi)006:61: mchog thun dgongs pa la mkhas 'gyur //
NK033(gi)006:62: dben pa'i gnas su gcig pur 'dug /
NK033(gi)006:63: lus kyi sngon 'gro bya ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)006:64: rigs drug spyod pa sna tshogs spyad //
NK033(gi)006:65: dkon mchog gsum gyi spyod pa'ang bya //
NK033(gi)006:66: skyil krung mthil sprad drang por bsrang //
NK033(gi)006:67: spyi bor thal mo sbyar bar bya //
NK033(gi)006:68: de ltar lus kyis sus byas pa //
NK033(gi)006:69: lus de mi ldog bar chad zhi //
NK033(gi)006:70: zhen pa bzlog cing sgrib pa 'dag /
NK033(gi)006:71: lus de sprul pa'i skur grol nas //
NK033(gi)006:72: sangs rgyas sku dang gnyis su med //
NK033(gi)006:74: ngag gi sngon 'gro bya ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)006:75: rigs drug sgra skad sna tshogs brjod //
NK033(gi)006:76: zhi khro'i sgra dang 'byung ba'i sgra //
NK033(gi)006:77: rnam pa sna tshogs nyid la spyad //
NK033(gi)006:78: rgyas gdab gnad la zhag gsum bya //
NK033(gi)006:79: rtsal sbyang mnyen btsal lam du gzhug /
NK033(gi)006:80: de ltar ngag gis sus byas pa //
NK033(gi)006:81: zhen log ngag gi sgrib pa 'dag /
NK033(gi)006:82: mi ldog gnyis med longs skur grol //
NK033(gi)006:83: yid kyi sngon 'gro bya ba'i phyir //
NK033(gi)006:84: rigs drug sdug bsngal blo la blang //
NK033(gi)006:85: de nas sems kyi byung ba btsal //
NK033(gi)006:86: ma rnyed chos kyi sku dang 'phrad //
NK033(gi)006:87: de nas sems kyi gnas pa btsal //
NK033(gi)006:88: ma rnyed longs spyod sku dang 'phrad //
NK033(gi)006:89: de nas sems kyi 'gro ba btsal //
NK033(gi)006:90: ma rnyed sprul pa'i sku dang 'phrad //
NK033(gi)006:91: de ltar sems kyis sus byas pa //
NK033(gi)006:92: zhen log bar chad zhi ba dang //
NK033(gi)006:93: sgrib dag khams gsum ldog pa med //
NK033(gi)006:94: chos kyi skur grol gnyis med 'da' //
NK033(gi)006:95: de nas lus ngag yid gsum po //
NK033(gi)006:96: rnal du 'bebs la mkhas par bya //
NK033(gi)006:97: des ni gsum po sor chud nas //
NK033(gi)006:98: nyams len nyid la brtson par 'gyur //
NK033(gi)006:99: de ltar sngon 'gro rdzogs byas nas //
NK033(gi)006:100: de dag blo yis bor nas kyang //
NK033(gi)006:101: mngon sum gnad la dbab pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)006:102: lus ngag yid gsum bya ba spang //
NK033(gi)006:103: 'di ni dur khrod chen po me ri 'bar ba'i
NK033(gi)006:104: shar phyogs d+aa ki ma sna tshogs 'du ba'i gnas
NK033(gi)006:105: su / yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yongs
NK033(gi)006:106: su mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul bstan pa'i tshe
NK033(gi)006:107: su / / dga' rab rdo rje sa la 'gyel te gdung ba'i smre sngags phyungs pa /
NK033(gi)006:108: kye ma kyi hud kye ma klong //
NK033(gi)006:109: ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub na //
NK033(gi)006:110: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel //
NK033(gi)006:111: zhes brjod de brgyal sangs pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:112: mdun gyi nam mkhar 'od phung gi dkyil du /
NK033(gi)006:113: phyag g.yas pa'i gru mo man chad phyung nas /
NK033(gi)006:114: bee d+aur+ya'i zhun ma nyid la rin po che lnga'i yi ge rang byung du bkod pa /
NK033(gi)006:115: rin po che shel gyi za ma tog dang bcas pa babs pa /
NK033(gi)006:116: byin rlabs chen po mchog gi yi ge /
NK033(gi)006:117: sangs rgyas kyi zhal chems gnyis pa /
NK033(gi)006:118: sprul pa po dga' rab rdo rje gzung ba'i don du snang bar byas pas /
NK033(gi)006:119: mya ngan las 'das ba thams cad kyi sna khrid dang 'dra ba /
NK033(gi)006:120: bstan pa thams cad kyi bcud bsdus shing bu gcig par bstan pa'o //
NK033(gi)006:123: bud+d+ha d+he ka ra ya tri n+aa ma /
NK033(gi)006:125: sangs rgyas kyi 'das rjes gsum pa /
NK033(gi)006:126: rang grol rdo rje 'chang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)006:127: kye ma kye ma rigs kyi bu rnams gson cig /
NK033(gi)006:129: sku gsum bzhugs stangs nyid la bslab //
NK033(gi)006:130: 'di ltar su yis byas pa ni //
NK033(gi)006:131: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK033(gi)006:132: sku yi klong du mya ngan 'da' //
NK033(gi)006:133: ngag ni bslab bya'i rim pa dang //
NK033(gi)006:134: gnas pa brtan zhing la yang bzla //
NK033(gi)006:135: de las mi 'da' sus byas pa //
NK033(gi)006:136: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK033(gi)006:137: gsung gi klong du mya ngan 'da' //
NK033(gi)006:138: sems gnad gzigs stangs gsum gcun te //
NK033(gi)006:139: yul gnad nam mkha' rkyen bral la //
NK033(gi)006:140: sgo gnad zlog phab zur gyis lta //
NK033(gi)006:141: rlung gnad shin tu dal la brlab //
NK033(gi)006:142: de ltar gnad gsum gzir ba yis //
NK033(gi)006:143: sku gsum rig pa stong par 'char //
NK033(gi)006:144: lug rgyu rig pa btson du bzung //
NK033(gi)006:145: mngon sum gnad mthong bzlog pa med //
NK033(gi)006:146: chos nyid mngon sum snang ba yis //
NK033(gi)006:147: yid dpyod 'dzin pa'i lta ba nub //
NK033(gi)006:148: gong du 'phel ba'i nyams snang gis //
NK033(gi)006:149: bar do'i ye shes mngon du byas //
NK033(gi)006:150: rig pa tshad phebs snang ba yis //
NK033(gi)006:151: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ngos zin //
NK033(gi)006:152: chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba yis //
NK033(gi)006:153: rdzogs chen bya bral 'bras bu thob //
NK033(gi)006:154: 'di ltar bzhi la mthar phyin na //
NK033(gi)006:155: myang 'das gzhan du btsal mi dgos //
NK033(gi)006:156: mi 'gul gsum la gzhi bcas pas //
NK033(gi)006:157: sdod pa gsum la tshad zin te //
NK033(gi)006:158: rtags ni lus ngag yid la 'byung //
NK033(gi)006:159: thob pa gsum gyi gzer thebs so //
NK033(gi)006:160: de las bstan du med do sa ma ya //
NK033(gi)006:161: bstan pa gang babs rin chen gyis //
NK033(gi)006:162: legs bris mchan khung dag tu bcang //
NK033(gi)006:163: bkur sti sus byas grol bar nges //
NK033(gi)006:165: sad ser mu ge gzas zin dus //
NK033(gi)006:166: phyogs bstun lce yis 'di bklag na //
NK033(gi)006:167: stong gsum sprul pa'i sangs rgyas la //
NK033(gi)006:168: yon phul ba bas 'di don che //
NK033(gi)006:169: bstan pa thams cad kyi rang babs rang byung byin rlabs kyi yi ge 'di /
NK033(gi)006:170: rgyal po dza ri zhes bya ba'i khab kyi lho /
NK033(gi)006:171: bya rgod spungs pa'i ri la ston pa mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul bstan pa'i tshe /
NK033(gi)006:172: dga' rab rdo rjes gdung ba'i smre sngags phyungs pas /
NK033(gi)006:173: rin po che lnga yi yi ge rang byung ba
NK033(gi)006:174: dga' rab rdo rje'i phyag g.yas pa'i mthil du babs
NK033(gi)006:175: pa / sangs rgyas kyi 'da' rjes tha ma bstan pa thams cad kyi bu gcig par bkod pa'o //
NK033(gi)006:178: lam bden pa thams cad kyi mthar thug pa 'od
NK033(gi)006:179: gsal rdzogs pa chen po sde gsum gyi yang rtse
NK033(gi)006:181: phyi nang gsang ba yang gsang gi skor mtha' yas par bzhugs pa las /
NK033(gi)006:182: yang gsang man ngag snying tig gi rgyud sho lo
NK033(gi)006:183: ka 'bum phrag drug cu rtsa bzhir grags pa'i snying
NK033(gi)006:184: po ni 'od kyi yang zhun bcu bdun bshad /
NK033(gi)006:185: ces gsungs pa ltar rgyud bcu bdun yin la /
NK033(gi)006:186: de thams cad kyi gazhi'am rtsa ba lta bur gyur
NK033(gi)006:187: pa rin po che 'byung ba'i sa bon lta bu
NK033(gi)006:188: ni / sgra thal 'gyur chen po rtsa ba'i rgyud
NK033(gi)006:189: nyid du rnam par bzhag cing de rnams mtha' dag
NK033(gi)006:190: gi gnad kyi snying po sangs rgyas kyi 'das rjes
NK033(gi)006:191: gsum du grags pa'i rgyud sde khyad par can dang
NK033(gi)006:192: ni / / rig 'dzin bzhi'i 'das rjes zhar byung
NK033(gi)006:193: dang bcas pa'i rdo rje'i tshig rkang rnams su 'du
NK033(gi)006:194: ni / / ba las / dang po 'das rjes
NK033(gi)006:195: rnam pa gsum gyis don gyi dgongs pa ji lta
NK033(gi)006:197: 'das rjes dang por rdzogs pa chen po man ngag
NK033(gi)006:198: sde'i gsang ba thun mong ma yin pa 'od gsal
NK033(gi)006:199: thig le chen po thod rgal gyi gdams pa gtso
NK033(gi)006:200: bor gyur pa'i man ngag gi lus yongs su rdzogs
NK033(gi)006:201: pa mdor bstan / gnyis pas de'i sngon 'gro dang /
NK033(gi)006:202: gsum pas dngos gzhi snang ba bzhi'i sa mtshams dang bcas rgyas par bshad pa ste /
NK033(gi)006:203: 'di rnams kyi don rgyas par kun mkhyen chen po'i gzhung theg mchog rin po che'i mdzod dang /
NK033(gi)006:204: man ngag gi yi ge yang tig yid bzhin nor
NK033(gi)006:205: bu sogs kyis mtshon khrid yig rnams las rtogs par
NK033(gi)006:206: bya'o // rig 'dzin bzhi'i zhal chems gser yig can /
NK033(gi)006:208: dga' rab rdo rje'i zhal chems tshig gsum gnad du brdeg pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)006:210: rang rig rtogs pa'i gding la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)006:211: yin par grub pa med pa'i rig pa 'di //
NK033(gi)006:212: rang snang 'char tshul cir yang ma 'gags pas //
NK033(gi)006:213: snang srid kun kyang chos sku'i zhing du shar //
NK033(gi)006:214: shar ba de nyid rang gi thog tu grol //
NK033(gi)006:215: de don bde gshegs kun gyi dgongs 'dus pa //
NK033(gi)006:216: brgyal ba bslang phyir tshig gsum man ngag 'di //
NK033(gi)006:217: 'khor 'das gnyis kyi gdos thag bcad pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)006:218: 'chi kha'i zhal chems snying gi dkyil du sbos //
NK033(gi)006:220: rig pa spyi brtol du bstan pa'i man ngag ni /
NK033(gi)006:221: ngo 1rang thog tu sprad pa dang //
NK033(gi)006:222: 2thag gcig thog tu bcad pa dang //
NK033(gi)006:233: gcig thog tu gcig rang 'phrad pa'o //
NK033(gi)006:234: rig pa gcig pu rang dang 'brel ba /
NK033(gi)006:235: rang gcig pu rang dang 'brel ba /
NK033(gi)006:236: grol ba gcig pu rang dang 'brel ba'o //
NK033(gi)006:237: rang thog tu mthar snang gi thag chod /
NK033(gi)006:238: gcig thog tu rang snang gi thag chod /
NK033(gi)006:239: grol thog tu the tshom gyi thag chod pa'o //
NK033(gi)006:241: rang la byan tshud pa phyug po'i bang mdzod lta bu'i gding /
NK033(gi)006:242: gzhan la byan tshud pa 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po lta bu'i gding /
NK033(gi)006:243: grol sa la byan tshud pa mkha' la mkha' thim pa lta bu'i gding ngo //
NK033(gi)006:249: rang ngo shes pas gzhi dang ngo 'phrad pa'o //
NK033(gi)006:250: de'i phyir na ma dang bu 'phrad pa lta bu
NK033(gi)006:251: ste grol sa gcig pu yin par ngo shes pa'o
NK033(gi)006:252: // rang gis rang grol bar shes pas thog ma rig pa nyid la thag bcad pa'o //
NK033(gi)006:253: de'i phyir dri mas dri ma 'khru ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:254: rnam rtog nyid la rnam rtog ste gnyen po gzhan la rag ma lus par thag bcad do //
NK033(gi)006:255: gzhi nyid las grol bas gding gang yin du bca' ba'o //
NK033(gi)006:256: de'i phyir sbrul gyi mdud pa nyid sbrul rang gis grol ba lta bu ste /
NK033(gi)006:257: gzhan ltos kyi rig pa tshi chad pas /
NK033(gi)006:258: dngos gzhi rang thog tu gzhi bca' ba'o //
NK033(gi)006:260: dga' rab rdo rje yongs su mya ngan las 'da' ba'i tshul bstan pa'i tshe /
NK033(gi)006:261: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen brgyal zhing sa la 'gyel nas
NK033(gi)006:262: kye ma kyi hud ces sgra chen po phyungs pas
NK033(gi)006:263: / ro langs bde ba 'od kyi dkyil nas phyag g.yas pa phyungs te /
NK033(gi)006:264: brgyal ba slong ba'i don du gsang ba'i zhal chems tshig gsum gnad du brdeg pa /
NK033(gi)006:265: phyag g.yas pa'i mthil du bee d+aur+ya mthing kha zhun mas rang nan du bris pa babs te /
NK033(gi)006:266: rin po che shel gyi za ma tog sen gang ba gcig snod du babs pas /
NK033(gi)006:267: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen brgyal ba las grol bar gyur cing /
NK033(gi)006:268: rtogs pa'i gding dang ldan par gyur to //
NK033(gi)006:269: de'i phyir na thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du sba bar bya'o //
NK033(gi)006:270: 'chi kha ma'i zhal gdams tshig gsum rgyud thams cad kyi bcud phyungs pa /
NK033(gi)006:271: lta ba'i don gser lta bur bstan pa /
NK033(gi)006:272: dur khrod chen po bsil ba tshal du babs pa /
NK033(gi)006:273: chu bo dan tig gi mgor snang bar byas pa'i gdams ngag dam pa /
NK033(gi)006:274: sems can thams cad dbugs 'byin par byed pa'i lam /
NK033(gi)006:275: sangs rgyas kyi zhing du skad cig la grol bar byed pa'i man ngag rdzogs so //
NK033(gi)006:276: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi zhal chems sgom nyams drug pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)006:278: rang rig rtogs pa'i gding la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)006:279: yin par grub pa med pa'i rig pa 'di //
NK033(gi)006:280: rang snang 'char tshul cir yang ma nges pas //
NK033(gi)006:281: snang srid kun kyang chos sku'i zhing du 'char //
NK033(gi)006:282: shar ba de nyid rang gi thog tu grol //
NK033(gi)006:283: de don bde gshegs kun gyi dgongs pa ni //
NK033(gi)006:284: brgyal ba bslang phyir tshig drug man ngag ni //
NK033(gi)006:285: 'khor 'das gnyis kyi gdos thag bcad pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)006:286: 'chi ka'i zhal chems snying gi dkyil du sbos //
NK033(gi)006:287: sa ma ya ma ti kra ma th+aa /
NK033(gi)006:288: dgongs pa rang gnas gding la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)006:289: don gyi dgongs pa ye shes chen po'i lung //
NK033(gi)006:290: 'di ni 1snang ba'i ye shes chen po de //
NK033(gi)006:291: ri dwags rgya la ji ltar 2tshud pa bzhin //
NK033(gi)006:292: bya byed 3bral ba'i mkha' la brtag par byos //
NK033(gi)006:293: ji ltar bdag gi blo la dgongs shar ba'i //
NK033(gi)006:294: brgyal ba bslang phyir don gyi dgongs pa 'di //
NK033(gi)006:295: rig pa'i gtad sa lus kyi gnad dang bstun //
NK033(gi)006:296: dgongs don man ngag drug gis phyed nas bstan //
NK033(gi)006:297: kye ma kye ma rigs kyi bu chen po //
NK033(gi)006:298: don gyi rig pa gcer bu mngon sum du lta bar 'dod na /
NK033(gi)006:306: gtad pa'i 'ben la dbyings 4gzud pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:307: mi 'gul ba la gzhi 5 bca' ba dang //
NK033(gi)006:308: rgya che ba nam 6mkha' spar gyis bzung dbyings rig 'dres pa /
NK033(gi)006:310: thog ma ka dag babs kyi yul dang /
NK033(gi)006:311: 'khrul pa snang ba lhun grub kyi yul dang /
NK033(gi)006:312: gnad brten pa yul gyi yul dang /
NK033(gi)006:313: nyams su blang bya nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba'i yul dang /
NK033(gi)006:314: gsal ba dngos snang kha dog 'od kyi yul dang /
NK033(gi)006:315: tha ma 'gro sa rang snang bar do'i yul lo //
NK033(gi)006:316: 1 seng ge'i 'dug stangs kyis rig pa gcun pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:317: glang po che'i 'dug stangs kyis lta ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:318: 'dab chags kyi lding thabs kyis lta ba spyi rgya rlabs kyis gcod pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:319: wa mo'i zur 'gros kyis sa mnan pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:320: skyes bu'i rgyang thabs kyis bar snang du yid tsam bzung ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:321: rgya mdud kyi dril lugs kyis lu gu rgyud kyi khungs bcad pa'o //
NK033(gi)006:322: 2 kha sna'i dbugs yid tsam nang du 'then pas ma rig pa las kyi rlung ldog /
NK033(gi)006:323: shes pa nam mkha' la gtad pas rnam rtog gi 'grul chod /
NK033(gi)006:324: rig pa mig tu bcug pas ngo bo la 'khrul pa med /
NK033(gi)006:325: dbyings phyi nang 'dres pas rig pa la 'gro sa med /
NK033(gi)006:326: de nyid dbyings dang ma bral bas yid kyi rnam rtog chod /
NK033(gi)006:327: rig pa dbyings dang 'dres pas 'khrul pa gzhi las sangs pa'o //
NK033(gi)006:328: 3 nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:329: dbyings rnam par dag pa dri ma dang bral ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:330: snang ba sgrib g.yogs dang bral ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:331: thig le spro bsdu dang bral ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:332: 'od snang gsal 'grib dang bral ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:333: lu gu rgyud 'gro 'ong dang bral ba la rang gi de bzhin nyid la gtad pa'o //
NK033(gi)006:334: 4 lus mi 'gul bas snang ba bzhi la bzhag pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:335: mig mi 'gul bas lu gu rgyud la gzer thebs pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:336: rig pa ma 'gul bas snang srid chos skur grol ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:337: de nyid ma 'gul bas 'khrul ba'i snang ba rgyun chad pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:338: de ltar chos sku 'gul ba med pas ye shes ngos zin pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:339: stong pa las 'gul ba med pas 'gyu byed rang sar dwangs pa'o //
NK033(gi)006:340: 5 snang srid rig stong gsal bar shar bas bem po las grol pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:341: nam mkha'i khams su lu gu rgyud kyis khyab pas chos nyid ma thog tu grol ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:342: cir snang 'od snang las ma 'das pas 'byung ba lnga'i bdud las grol ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:343: 'khor 'das rang ngo shes pas ltos pa'i chos las grol ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:344: stong pa gsal ba rig pa 'dres pas rgyud lung gi tshig las grol ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:345: dag pa'i dbyings rgya bskyed pa'i rig pa rang thog tu spar gyis zin pa zhes bya'o //
NK033(gi)006:347: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen dgongs pa yongs su mya ngan
NK033(gi)006:348: las 'das pa'i tshe 'od zer gyi phung po dang
NK033(gi)006:349: bcas te nam mkha' la gshegs pa sh+r+ai sim ha
NK033(gi)006:350: brgyal zhing sa la 'gyel bar gyur te kyi hud
NK033(gi)006:351: kyi sgra chen po phyogs bcur 'bod cing gnas pa
NK033(gi)006:352: las / nam mkhar sgra chen po zhig grags par gyur te /
NK033(gi)006:353: de nyid kyis brgyal sangs nas bltas pas nam mkha' 'od phung gi dkyil nas /
NK033(gi)006:354: many+dzu sh+r+ais phyag g.yas pa phyungs te brgyal ba bslang ba'i don du /
NK033(gi)006:355: sh+r+ai sim ha'i phyag mthil du rin po che'i za
NK033(gi)006:356: ma tog gi nang du bee d+aur+ya mthing kha zhun
NK033(gi)006:357: mas rang nan du bris pa gcig dur khrod chen
NK033(gi)006:358: po so sa gling de nyid du babs so //
NK033(gi)006:359: de nyid babs pa tsam gyis rtogs pa'i gding dang ldan par gyur to //
NK033(gi)006:360: 'di ni 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi zhal chems sgom
NK033(gi)006:361: nyams drug gis skye med stong pa'i klong du mya
NK033(gi)006:362: ngan las 'da' bar byed pa'i man ngag gsang ba
NK033(gi)006:363: bas kyang ches gsang bar gyur pa /
NK033(gi)006:364: nyams su blang ba'i phyogs su bstan pa rdzogs so //
NK033(gi)006:365: sh+r+ai sim ha'i zhal chems gzer bu bdun pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)006:367: stong gsal shes rab rdzogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)006:368: kun tu khyab 1cing sna tshogs 2snang ba yis //
NK033(gi)006:369: rig 3pa'i ye shes 4rgya yan 5 phyogs 6med de //
NK033(gi)006:370: mi 7'gyur ba la gzer chen btab pa'i phyir //
NK033(gi)006:371: 'khor 'das 'phrang la gzer chen bdun btab pas //
NK033(gi)006:372: mi 'gyur bde chen bdag gi blo la shar //
NK033(gi)006:373: de don man ngag nyi ma'i zer 'dra ba //
NK033(gi)006:374: brgyal ba bslang phyir dgongs don gsang ba 'di //
NK033(gi)006:375: gsal ba'i shes rab mdzod kyi sgo phye la //
NK033(gi)006:376: yid bzhin nor 'dra'i don 'di rtogs par gyis //
NK033(gi)006:377: gsal ba'i ye shes zang thal gyi 1gzer gyis 'khor 'das gnyis kyi mtshams su thob cig /
NK033(gi)006:378: sgron ma rang snang gi 2gzer gyis yul sems gnyis kyi bar du thob cig /
NK033(gi)006:379: ngo bo rang dag gi 3gzer blo dngos gnyis kyi bar du thob cig /
NK033(gi)006:380: lta ba grol yan gyi 4 gzer rtag chad gnyis kyi bar du thob cig /
NK033(gi)006:381: rig pa chos nyid kyi 5gzer chos can chos nyid kyi bar du thob cig /
NK033(gi)006:382: sgo lnga rgya yan gyi 6 gzer bying rgod gnyis kyi bar la thob cig /
NK033(gi)006:383: chos sku ye rdzogs kyi 7gzer snang stong gnyis kyi bar la thob cig /
NK033(gi)006:385: gsal ba rang ngos ma sgrib pa shes rab rang
NK033(gi)006:386: grol gzhan ngo la bzhag pa ni r+ts+wa dang me
NK033(gi)006:388: snang ba gcer grol du shes pas dran bsam la
NK033(gi)006:389: byan tshud pa ni mun khang dang snang ba 'phrad
NK033(gi)006:390: pa lta bu'o // rig pa ye dag gi dgongs
NK033(gi)006:391: pa gzhi mngon du shes pa ni yid mthun pa'i
NK033(gi)006:393: rang ngo phyogs bral gyi ye shes rang rkyen du
NK033(gi)006:394: shar bas yin min gyi rtsis las 'das pa bzhin
NK033(gi)006:395: dang me long 'phrad pa lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)006:396: lta sgom las grol ba'i rtog pa sna tshogs rol
NK033(gi)006:397: par shar bas ba mo dang nyi ma reg pa
NK033(gi)006:398: lta bu'o // snang srid sor bzhag gi dgongs pa
NK033(gi)006:399: ye rgyas btab pas yul can mnyam pa nyid du
NK033(gi)006:400: shes pa ni bu gcig po dang 'phrad pa lta
NK033(gi)006:401: lta bu'o // bu'o // chos sku 'bad rtsol med
NK033(gi)006:402: par ye nas rang dang 'du 'bral med pa yin
NK033(gi)006:403: pas snod bcud rang sar grol ba ni dbul po
NK033(gi)006:404: gter mdzod dang 'phrad pa lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)006:406: sh+r+ai sim ha dgongs pa yongs su mya ngan las
NK033(gi)006:407: 'das pa'i tshe 'od zer gyi phung po dang bcas
NK033(gi)006:408: te nam mkha' la gshegs pas /
NK033(gi)006:409: ye shes mdo brgyal zhing sa la 'gyel bar gyur te kye ma kyi hud kyi sgra bsgrags pas /
NK033(gi)006:410: nam mkha' la sgra chen po grags te /
NK033(gi)006:411: de nyid kyis brgyal sangs nas bltas pas /
NK033(gi)006:412: 'od kyi dkyil nas phyag g.yas pa phyungs te /
NK033(gi)006:413: ye shes mdo brgyal ba las bslang ba'i don du
NK033(gi)006:414: rin po che'i za ma tog sen gang ba gcig
NK033(gi)006:416: de nyid babs pa tsam gyis rtogs pa dang ldan par gyur to //
NK033(gi)006:417: bkra shis khri sgor babs pa /
NK033(gi)006:418: sh+r+ai sim ha'i zhal chems gzer bu bdun pa long ba'i sna khrid dang 'dra ba rdzogs so //
NK033(gi)006:419: ye shes mdo'i zhal chems bzhag thabs bzhi pa bzhugs so //
NK033(gi)006:421: stong pa ye dag ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK033(gi)006:422: gsang sngags gsang ba'i mdo don 'dir snang ba //
NK033(gi)006:423: dus gsum bzhugs pa'i thugs kyi dgongs shar ba //
NK033(gi)006:424: blo yi mun sel sgron ma 'od po che //
NK033(gi)006:425: 'jig rten rab rib rnams ni bsal bya'i phyir //
NK033(gi)006:426: rang rig ye shes rtogs dka' kun spangs ba //
NK033(gi)006:427: 'gyur med thabs kyi rgya yis gzung byas te //
NK033(gi)006:428: rgya che rab zab dbyings su bcug nas kyang //
NK033(gi)006:429: mtha' bral nyag gcig ngang du bzhag par byos //
NK033(gi)006:430: brgyal ba rnams ni 'di yis dbugs phyungs te //
NK033(gi)006:431: sangs rgyas rnams dang mnyam pa nyid du grags //
NK033(gi)006:432: gang zhig bzung bas ma zin rig pa de //
NK033(gi)006:433: de nyid 'dzin 'dod skal ldan blo che ba /
NK033(gi)006:434: yi ge 'di la rtag tu goms par gyis //
NK033(gi)006:435: e ma hoh 'di la rtag tu goms par byas na bde ba shugs la 'byung ngo //
NK033(gi)006:436: kye ma mnyam pa chen po'i sa thob par 'dod 'di nyid la rtag tu goms par gyis shig /
NK033(gi)006:437: spyod pa thams cad la rtsal sbyong bar 'dod na /
NK033(gi)006:438: snang ba cog 1bzhag gis snang ba thams cad cer bzhag tu zhog cig /
NK033(gi)006:439: sgom pa thams cad la stobs rnyed par 'dod na /
NK033(gi)006:440: rgya mtsho cog 2bzhag gi dgongs pas blo dngos gnyis gcig tu dril la zhog cig /
NK033(gi)006:441: lta ba thams cad las rang grol bar 'dod na /
NK033(gi)006:442: ri bo cog 3bzhag gi lta bas chos thams cad zad sar skyol zhig /
NK033(gi)006:443: 'bras bu thams cad rang sar gnas par 'dod na /
NK033(gi)006:444: rig pa cog 4bzhag gi lta bas man ngag la
NK033(gi)006:445: 'khrul pa thams cad rang sar grol bar zhog cig
NK033(gi)006:446: / snang ba rang bzhag yin pas ye nas stong pa dang 'brel ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:447: blo rang sar bzhag pas ye nas dngos po dang 'brel ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:448: chos rnams rang sar bzhag pas dbyings rig dang 'brel ba dang /
NK033(gi)006:449: 'khrul pa thams cad cog bzhag yin pas ye nas rang grol dang 'brel pa'o //
NK033(gi)006:450: wal po rjes med chu yi ri mo lta bus snang ba gcig thog tu gcig bzhag pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:451: dran pa rjes med mkha' la bya 'phur ba lta
NK033(gi)006:452: bus bsam pa gcig thog tu gcig bzhag pa dang
NK033(gi)006:453: / 'khrul pa rang dag mkha' 'gro rnyi las bton
NK033(gi)006:454: pa lta bus stong pa gcig thog tu gcig bzhag
NK033(gi)006:455: / pa dang / dag pa ldog med rims nad
NK033(gi)006:456: byang ba lta bus rig pa gcig thog tu gcig
NK033(gi)006:458: snang ba spyod cing bsgyur nus pa chang dang ra
NK033(gi)006:459: ro ba lta bus 'byung ba lnga rang sar bzhag
NK033(gi)006:460: pa dang / sems gnas shing tshad zin pa rngon
NK033(gi)006:461: pas ri dwags rgya la zin pa bzung ba lta
NK033(gi)006:462: bus sems rang sar bzhag pa dang /
NK033(gi)006:463: chos la mi gnas pa'i shes pas rig pa mthong
NK033(gi)006:464: ba bzhin dang me long lta bus chos thams cad
NK033(gi)006:466: 'khrul pa ma thog tu grol ba sbrul dang mdud
NK033(gi)006:467: pa lta bus 'khrul dang ma 'khrul med pa rang
NK033(gi)006:468: sar bzhag pa'o // snang ba rang grol ba gzu
NK033(gi)006:469: bo'i blo can lha khang du phyin pa lta bu'o
NK033(gi)006:470: sar bzhag pa'o // // bsam pa thams cad gzhi
NK033(gi)006:471: la thim pa rgya mtsho rlung gis ma bskyod pa
NK033(gi)006:472: sar bzhag pa'o // // lta bu'o // dbyings dang
NK033(gi)006:473: rig pa rang 'phrad pa ri rgyal gyi rtse mor
NK033(gi)006:475: sku gsum phyir mi ldog pa rang sa la sleb pa bse shing gi 'bras bu lta bu'o //
NK033(gi)006:476: lta sgom spyod pa'i srog shing yin //
NK033(gi)006:477: rengs pa rnams kyi gnya' gcog yin //
NK033(gi)006:478: stor ba rnams kyi rjes gcod yin //
NK033(gi)006:479: ltebs pa rnams kyi rgyangs shing yin //
NK033(gi)006:480: rgya che spar gyis bzung ba'i man ngag /
NK033(gi)006:481: da rmu rgod 'thur srab 'jug pa'i man ngag /
NK033(gi)006:482: rno la ngar gyis 'dogs pa'i man ngag /
NK033(gi)006:483: byas pa thams cad rang sar bzhag pa'i man ngag go //
NK033(gi)006:485: sna tshogs lam du khyer ba'i rkang //
NK033(gi)006:486: dran pa rgyun thag gcod pa'i lag /
NK033(gi)006:487: rig pa dngos la lta ba'i mig /
NK033(gi)006:488: 'khrul pa gzhi la dag pa'i khrus so //
NK033(gi)006:489: snang ba thug phrad kyi lam /
NK033(gi)006:490: rig pa thug phrad kyi gzhi /
NK033(gi)006:491: mthong ba thug phrad kyi yul /
NK033(gi)006:492: grol ba thug phrad kyi 'bras bu'o //
NK033(gi)006:493: dz+ny+aa na s+au tra dgongs pa yongs su mya ngan las 'das ba'i tshe /
NK033(gi)006:494: bi ma la mi tra brgyal zhing sa la 'gyel
NK033(gi)006:495: te kye ma kyi hud kyi sgra chen po 'don
NK033(gi)006:496: zhing gnas pa las nam mkha' 'od phung gi dkyil
NK033(gi)006:497: nas sgra chen po grags te brgyal sangs nas bltas
NK033(gi)006:498: pas / phyag g.yas pa'i gru mo man chad phyungs te /
NK033(gi)006:499: bi ma la mi tra'i phyag g.yas pa'i mthil du
NK033(gi)006:500: rin po che'i za ma tog sen gang ba gcig
NK033(gi)006:501: babs so // de zhal phyes nas gzigs pas bee
NK033(gi)006:502: d+aur+ya mthing kas rang nan du rin po che lnga'i
NK033(gi)006:503: shog bu la bris pa gcig bzhugs 'dug ste /
NK033(gi)006:504: bi ma las bltas pa tsam gyis rtogs pa'i gding dang ldan par gyur to //
NK033(gi)006:505: dur khrod chen po b+ha seng du snang bar byas pa /
NK033(gi)006:506: ye shes mdo'i zhal chems bzhag thabs bzhis rten gcig la 'tshang rgya bar byed pa /
NK033(gi)006:507: mun khung gi sgron me dang 'dra ba rdzogs so //
NK033(gi)006:511: 'bras bu rang bzhag gi gdams ngag go //
NK033(gi)006:514: rig 'dzin bzhi'i zhal chems dang pos khregs chod thod rgal gnyis ka'i ngo sprod rtsa ba ston /
NK033(gi)006:515: gnyis pas thod rgal gyi sgom pa gtso bor ston /
NK033(gi)006:516: gsum pas bogs 'byin dang gegs sel ston //
NK033(gi)006:517: bzhi pas khregs chod kyi bzhag thabs gtso bor ston /
NK033(gi)006:518: bzhi kas kyang bzhi ka ston pas na gang zag
NK033(gi)006:519: gcig 'tshang rgya ba'i lam gyi cha rkyen rdzogs par
